"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/522032","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2016-06-10","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer given by the Minister for the Cabinet Office on 8 June 2016 to Question <a href="http://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/written-questions-answers-statements/written-question/Commons/2016-05-26/38811/" target="_blank">38811</a>.</p>","Wantage","Mr Edward Vaizey",,"2016-06-10T08:54:13.58Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/522032/answer","Biography information for Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/522032/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/522032/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2016-05-26","Department for Culture, Media and Sport: UK Membership of EU","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, if he will place in the Library copies of all letters, leaflets and other material from his Department circulated to (a) stakeholders and (b) members of the public on the EU Referendum; what the costs of the production and distribution of that material has been since 1 January 2016; and what he estimates the cost of any further production and distribution of such material will be between 6 May 2016 and 23 June 2016.","false","Biography information for Mr William Wragg","Hazel Grove","William Wragg","38813"
